sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as TaskController
    participant Service as TaskService
    participant Cache as Redis
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant SubTaskService

    Note over Client,SubTaskService: Create Task Flow

    Client->>API: POST /tasks
    API->>Service: create(taskData)
    Service->>DB: insert(task)
    DB-->>Service: savedTask
    Service->>Cache: set(task:id:detail, savedTask, 5min)
    Service-->>API: savedTask
    API-->>Client: 201 Created + task

    Note over Client,SubTaskService: Get Tasks Flow

    Client->>API: GET /tasks/my
    API->>Service: getTasksByUserId(userId)
    Service->>Cache: get(task:user:tasks)
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>Service: cachedTasks
        Service-->>API: cachedTasks
        API-->>Client: 200 OK + tasks
    else Cache Miss
        Service->>DB: find({ownerUserId/assignedUserIds})
        DB-->>Service: tasks
        Service->>Cache: set(task:user:tasks, tasks, 2min)
        Service-->>API: tasks
        API-->>Client: 200 OK + tasks
    end

    Note over Client,SubTaskService: Add SubTask Flow

    Client->>API: POST /tasks/:id/subtasks
    API->>Service: addSubtask(taskId, title, order, userId)
    Service->>SubTaskService: createSubTask(dto, userId)
    SubTaskService->>DB: insert(subTask)
    SubTaskService->>DB: update(task.totalSubtasks)
    DB-->>SubTaskService: savedSubTask
    SubTaskService-->>Service: subTask
    Service->>Cache: del(task:id:detail)
    Service-->>API: subTask
    API-->>Client: 201 Created + subTask

    Note over Client,SubTaskService: Update Task Status Flow

    Client->>API: PUT /tasks/:id/status
    API->>Service: updateTaskStatus(taskId, status)
    Service->>DB: updateOne({_id}, {status, completedTime})
    DB-->>Service: updatedTask
    Service->>Cache: del(task:id:detail)
    Service-->>API: updatedTask
    API-->>Client: 200 OK + task

    Note over Client,SubTaskService: Toggle SubTask Flow

    Client->>API: PUT /subtasks/:id/toggle
    API->>SubTaskService: toggleSubTaskStatus(id, isCompleted, userId)
    SubTaskService->>DB: updateOne(subTask)
    SubTaskService->>DB: updateStats(task.totalSubtasks, task.completedSubtasks)
    DB-->>SubTaskService: updatedSubTask
    SubTaskService->>Cache: del(task:id:detail)
    SubTaskService-->>API: subTask
    API-->>Client: 200 OK + subTask
